Terrorsaur:



Terrorsaur looked back. He then made a decision to close the doors on the 
cave. He slid it over until they closed as good as he could get it. The 
Maximals out there would now have to deal with the acid rain alone. He 
looked over. He needed repairs badly. He had damage from Rowdy Wolf, the 
Dinobots, and the acid rain. He flew up and went to the CR tanks in the 
back.
